description: For sale: $74,900. If you're looking for a great getaway in north-central MN, look no further. This year-round cabin on 4.3 acres could be yours, but don't wait. Priced to sell and it is a steal!  Located in Goodland, MN, just north of Swan River, this property is just off freshly-paved Hwy 65.  Only 2-1/2 hour commute from the twin cities. This cabin comes with 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, full kitchen, dining room, & spacious living room, & forced air furnace. The septic system was upgraded with a new tank & mound a few years back. Yard is open with mature trees surrounding.  Excellent hunting & recreation opportunities as well.  A 277 pound, 24-point buck was taken just off this property by the nearby swamp.  See the "Cortese Buck" story attached to this listing.  Ride on the nearby Goodland Trail (ATV/OHM) & the Alborn-Pengilly Trail (ATV).  There are many other Snowmobile & Multi-Use Motorized & Non-Motorized Trails nearby as well.  This could be your recreational home base, or your quiet getaway!

description: Recently sold: $215,500. Perfect property for the outdoor enthusiast!  3 bedroom home situated on over 56 acres of land backed up to thousands of acres of public land.  Follow the trail from this property through the field into tax forfeit land and right to Pancake Lake! Solid home with attached two stall garage, main floor laundry, spacious kitchen, living room and family room with electric fireplace.  Tons of storage, out buildings and separate 20x30 detached garage.  Landscaping includes, perennials, flowering crab trees and is dotted with nice oaks and pines.  The two large deer stands will stay with the property to boot!  Convenient location, close to snowmobile trails and other outdoor recreation.
